s\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"comforts\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"demons\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"deities\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"Cate McQuaid\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fragments of Time III\\\", he said, \\\"was completed through the inspiration and support of numerous forebears such as AD Scott, Barrington Watson, Osmond Watson, Ralph Campbell-those who made possible a generation of younger artists coming into being.\\\"\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anno_Domini\", \"score\": 0.9996155222513301, \"rank\": 0.00038145145989703884, \"text\": \"AD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anno_Domini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anno_Domini\"}, {\"begin\": 1659, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.9999984214583673, \"rank\": 1.4444483684917477e-06, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}, {\"begin\": 1666, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barrington_Watson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barrington Watson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barrington_Watson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barrington_Watson\"}, {\"begin\": 1685, \"end\": 1698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmond_Watson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Osmond Watson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmond_Watson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmond_Watson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fragments\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"Time III\", 